data.description: Single Family Residence +Additional 1,000 s/ft house in the back (ADU) Newly built, fully permitted detached 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, Additional Dwelling Unit posterior to the house. The front house is a single-family residence, remodeled through the years. It has laminate floors, tile in the kitchen, oak kitchen cabinets, newer windows with shutters in the living room, dining area, kitchen, bedrooms #1 and #3, fresh paint interior and exterior, fireplace in the living room, extra bath (bonus, buyer to verify permit), washer and dryer hookups in kitchen, ceiling fans, HVAC. ADU is newly built with plenty of space! The large living area of 1,000 s/f comes with an open floor plan, a sliding door to the dining area, a wide and inviting kitchen, new fixtures, new bathrooms, and two walk-in closets. The yards are drought tolerant as most areas have been cemented with only a quad garden between the houses and the grassy front lawn. Buyers to verify all permits and satisfy due diligence requirements on square footage, condition, and investigations.
